      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like such a heavy, useless weight to carry around every single day. if i was gone, there'd be no more struggle for me, and the world wouldn't even skip a beat. it seems almost kinder to just let go than to keep dragging this emptiness around. like, wouldn't it be better for everyone if things were just quiet?",
